description:
Let’s face it, nobody likes moles. 
That’s why TapTop is so cool, you can shoot at moles as much as you want without having to stop!

Enjoy 4 different types of moles [-two different classical moles that give you 5 points each;
-one football mole that gives you 15 points but that you have to shoot twice;
-one blind mole that makes you lose 8 points;
-a master-time mole that gives you 5 seconds of bonus time!
(next updates should bring other awesome moles!)], and, if you’re really crazy, try to beat our best score: 1142 points!

Good game and Good luck ;-)


For more informations about our next games and projects, you can follow @tafle on Twitter ;)
